Laga soo bilaabo bishii Febraayo 2009, Ciraaq waxay "macaansatay" shuruudaha ay bixiyeen shirkadaha shidaalka ee caalamiga ah oo doonaya in ay kobciyaan kaydka dalka ee tusaalaha ugu horreeya ee isbedelka caalamiga ah ee awoodda oo bilowda in lagu mariyo warshadaha saliidda.
